Talent artiste manager and entertainment personality, Soso Soberekon also known as White Lion has revealed he is crushing on reality star, Cynthia Nwadiora, popularly known as Cee-C. The ceo ‘WHITE LION GROUP’ revealed his crush on Cee-C during a question and answer session on his official Instagram page in an insta story. An inquisitive fan, who decided to know what’s going on between him and Cee-C, asked if he was in a romantic relationship with her. In response to this, the former manager of music label, “Five Star Music” admitted that for now, there is nothing of such but he wishes it could happen. He wrote; “NO SHE’S NOT, I WISH SHE IS.”  